description:
First off, the staff are extremely warm and inviting ... Some have worked here for over 10 years! Bring lots of cash and try many things!; 

Come early and stay late! I got here at noon and didn't leave for 2.5 hours and would've easily stayed longer and ordered more! 

This is a historical gem in SF, that you don't want to miss out on! If you are a wine snob, bring your own wine and get ready to enjoy this tiny-treasure!
